The files and patch in this folder are what it takes to load Aria.

Known about Aria: She assisted/gave hints to Link. Appeared at lake and in castle town. Dev period: A+C

Aria.ppf: the two files inserted into the game (see offsets in ../../offsets.txt)
Aria.zactor: Modified Malon actor. Changes: Changed object to 0x10, changed eye texture offsets.
Aria.zobj: Aria's object file appended to Malon's (Using ZOTag)

Known issues:
 - animation is a little funny, arm rotation needs to be fixed
 - eyes don't blink properly
 
That's all, feel free to add to her.
~spinout 2009-07-30 00:53:31
